# ğŸ¬ IMDB Movie Data Analysis

This project performs **Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)** on the [IMDB Movie Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets) using Python.  
The goal is to extract meaningful insights into **movie trends, ratings, revenues, and genre performance** through visual and statistical exploration.

---

## ğŸ“Š Project Objectives

- Understand the structure and contents of the IMDB dataset  
- Explore distributions of movie ratings, revenues, and metascores  
- Analyze **genre-based trends** and their correlations  
- Visualize insights using `matplotlib` and `seaborn`

---

## ğŸ“ Dataset Information

- **File Name:** `IMDB-Movie-Data.csv`  
- **Source:** [Kaggle IMDB Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets)  
- **Description:** Contains metadata for 1,000 popular IMDB movies, including:

  | Column | Description |
  |---------|-------------|
  | Title | Name of the movie |
  | Genre | Genre(s) of the movie |
  | Director | Movie director |
  | Actors | Leading actors |
  | IMDB Rating | Audience rating |
  | Metascore | Critic rating |
  | Revenue (Millions) | Box office revenue |
  | Year | Year of release |

---

